The following information should be included in the letter of conditions:  
To describe loan rates and terms:  
 The debt limit approved, the applicable interest rate, the loan term, and the amortization term;  
 Equity contribution requirements;  
 Initial 2 percent operating capital requirement;  
 A request for confirmation that the borrower will pay cost overruns;  
